title: 10/30/2020  HOUR 1 - Matt Ryan
itunes:title: 10/30/2020  HOUR 1 - Matt Ryan
description:
On today's episode's of the Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps Thursday Night's game between the Panthers and Falcons. Are the Falcons the best 2 win team we've seen? We're joined by Falcons QB Matt Ryan and DP also talks the fate of Clemson moving forward as Trevor Lawrence has tested positive for Covid-19.
